Chester, Respondent, v. Jumel et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. July 9, 1889.) For hearing on appeal, see 5 H. Y. Supp. 809, 819, 820, 822, 823.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

Ho opinion. Motion denied, with $10 costs and disbursements.
